item.description: Yes its the park again. We'll be hanging out playing fetch for about 90 minutes. Then we'll be moving on to Earl G Legacy park at 1 pm for a short hike around the woods. We'd love company. So if you'd like to join us please bring treats, toys and poop bags. Please be advised that I will cancel this Meetup if weather conditions warrant. So check the site before leaving. Be ready to have fun laughing at our four legged friends. Hope to see you. WOOF
